import React from 'react' import { useDispatch } from 'react-redux' import { dataRemove } from './Slice' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'; import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'; import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'; function Home() { const Profile = useSelector(state => state.usData.Pass) console.log("Profile", Profile); const p = Profile[0] const dispatch = useDispatch() const lo = () => { dispatch(dataRemove()) } return (
{p.username}
Email : {p.email}
Age : {p.age}
Address : {p.address}
) } export default Home
